Package: rPALM
Type: Package
Title: Create static and dynamic drivers for the urban climate model PALM4U
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sebastian Stadler
Maintainer: Sebastian Stadler <sebastian.stadler@ibp.fraunhofer.de>
Description: Provides R6-classes to create and edit static drivers for the urban climate
    model PALM4U. Multiple functions are provided to build a domain from scratch 
    or import rastered files from QGIS or ArcGIS. Simple plot functions are available as 
    well as LOD2 variables.
    There is also a prototype class to create a synthethic dynamic driver. Or not.
